00:10:51.740 --> 00:10:53.150
I have a young son.

00:10:53.150 --> 00:10:55.550
And I found the
beginning of that film--

00:10:55.550 --> 00:10:56.656
who's seen "Lion"?

00:10:56.656 --> 00:10:58.155
I don't know if
anyone could-- yeah.

00:10:58.155 --> 00:10:59.210
Oh, fabulous.

00:10:59.210 --> 00:10:59.780
That's great.

00:10:59.780 --> 00:11:00.280
Look.

00:11:00.280 --> 00:11:02.439
SAROO BRIERLEY:
Everyone at Google.

00:11:02.439 --> 00:11:03.980
CASEY WHITELAW:
Watching those scenes

00:11:03.980 --> 00:11:05.605
where you're lost on
the train and then

00:11:05.605 --> 00:11:07.820
surviving in Kolkata
